  "title": "Add unique selector to items in refinementList",
  "body": "I want to add some css to my facets links, so I need unique selector.\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/976175/10811530/17c193a8-7e0d-11e5-86be-85ae02f33c1d.png)\nSince Hogan doesn't support lambdas, I don't really see how I can manipulate the value in my template.\nA solution could be to map the facets but I think the widget could help me to achieve this common use case.\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/976175/10811651/7ecfaac0-7e0e-11e5-86dc-f9cc214c91f8.png)\n",
